  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Collections_EnumerableHelpers'>Class EnumerableHelpers    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Collections/EnumerableHelpers.cs#L39'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.html'>Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Internal helper functions for working with enumerables.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static class EnumerableHelpers</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.html'>EnumerableHelpers</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.memberwiseclone'>object.MemberwiseClone()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.GetEmptyEnumerator``1' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.GetEmptyEnumerator``1' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Collections_EnumerableHelpers_GetEmptyEnumerator__1'>GetEmptyEnumerator&lt;T&gt;()    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Collections/EnumerableHelpers.cs#L49'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets an enumerator singleton for an empty collection.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static IEnumerator&lt;T&gt; GetEmptyEnumerator&lt;T&gt;()</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.generic.ienumerator-1'>IEnumerator</a>&lt;T&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Type Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>T</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.Reset``1(``0@)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.Reset``1(``0@)' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Collections_EnumerableHelpers_Reset__1___0__'>Reset&lt;T&gt;(ref T)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Collections/EnumerableHelpers.cs#L43'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Calls Reset on an enumerator instance.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>internal static void Reset&lt;T&gt;(ref T enumerator) where T : IEnumerator</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>enumerator</code> T  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Type Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>T</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Remarks</h4><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Enables Reset to be called without boxing on a struct enumerator that lacks a public Reset.</p>\n<h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.ToArray``1(System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable{``0},System.Int32@)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.ToArray``1(System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable{``0},System.Int32@)' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Collections_EnumerableHelpers_ToArray__1_System_Collections_Generic_IEnumerable___0__System_Int32__'>ToArray&lt;T&gt;(IEnumerable&lt;T&gt;, out int)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Collections/EnumerableHelpers.cs#L58'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Converts an enumerable to an array using the same logic as List{T}.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static T[] ToArray&lt;T&gt;(IEnumerable&lt;T&gt; source, out int length)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>source</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.generic.ienumerable-1'>IEnumerable</a>&lt;T&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The enumerable to convert.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>length</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.int32'>int</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The number of items stored in the resulting array, 0-indexed.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> T[]  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The resulting array.  The length of the array may be greater than <code class=\"paramref\">length</code>,\nwhich is the actual number of elements in the array.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Type Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>T</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
